performa.overview.heading: Overview
performa.overview.description: Performance metrics provide an overall picture of the current live performance for the Dialer and Agents. The data is for a day based on the time zone that your browser is in.
performa.agentstatussummary.description: Agent Status Summary gives the count of agents in various states, only for logged-in agents. The data is refreshed every {{interval}} seconds.
performa.callstatussummary.description: Call Status Summary displays the live call stats. The Total Calls Connected to Agent and the Total Calls Connected to Machine are shown for the current day. The data is refreshed every {{interval}} seconds.
performa.agentstatedetail.description: Agent State Detail shows the logged-in agent’s current status – this is only for an individual agent. The data is refreshed every {{interval}} seconds.
performa.calldetail.description: The Call Detail section displays the live call stats. Calls disappear on 20 seconds after completion, with the latest call displayed at the top. The data is refreshed every {{interval}} seconds.
performa.campaignsummary.description: Campaign Summary shows the campaign-level performance. This displays both campaign-level predictive parameters and current dialer pace data. The data is refreshed every {{interval}} seconds.
